# 5. Consistent UI/UX System (Across All Activities)

## 🎯 Objective

Create a **simple, consistent, and usable UI system** for:

* MainActivity (Navigation)
* DeviceInfoActivity (Static Info)
* SensorLabActivity (Dynamic Interaction)
* ReportActivity (Readable Output)

Focus:

> Clarity > Fancy design
> Consistency > Complexity
> Function > Decoration

---

# 🧠 Core Design Principles

1. **Same layout logic everywhere**
2. **Predictable navigation**
3. **Readable information hierarchy**
4. **Minimal visual noise**
5. **Fast interaction (no lag, no clutter)**

---

# 🎨 1. Global Layout System

## 📱 Base Layout Pattern

```text id="9b7x2c"
Top Bar (Title)
↓
Content Area (Scrollable)
↓
Bottom Action / Buttons (optional)
```

---

## 🔹 Components Used Everywhere

* `TextView` → Labels & values
* `CardView` → Grouped sections
* `RecyclerView` → Lists (sensors)
* `ScrollView` → Long content
* `Button` → Actions

---

# 🧩 2. Visual Hierarchy (Critical)

## 🔹 Text Levels

```text id="c8x5qn"
Title → Large, bold
Section Header → Medium, bold
Label → Normal
Value → Slightly highlighted
```

---

## 🔹 Example

```text id="f0l8ks"
⚙️ Hardware

RAM        8 GB
Storage    128 GB
```

---

# 🎨 3. Color System (Minimal)

## 🎯 Keep it simple

| Element     | Color                         |
| ----------- | ----------------------------- |
| Background  | White / Dark (system default) |
| Text        | Black / White                 |
| Accent      | Single color (blue/green)     |
| Status Good | Green                         |
| Warning     | Orange                        |
| Error       | Red                           |

---

## ⚠️ Rule

* Don’t use too many colors
* Color = meaning, not decoration

---

# 🧭 4. Navigation Consistency

## 🔹 Back Behavior

* Always returns to previous screen
* No custom back logic

---

## 🔹 Entry Points

```text id="8lqg2r"
MainActivity → All modules
```

---

## 🔹 No Deep Nesting

* Max 2 levels:

```text id="pt4z0o"
Main → List → Detail
```

