# 🧠 7. Consistency Rules

1. Same padding everywhere (16dp recommended)
2. Same card style everywhere
3. Same font sizes across screens
4. Same button style across app

---

# 📏 8. Spacing System

```text id="q4w8zt"
Section gap → 16dp
Element gap → 8dp
Card padding → 16dp
```

---

# 🔤 9. Text Style Guidelines

* Avoid long paragraphs
* Use short lines
* Align labels and values
* Use icons sparingly

---

# ⚠️ 10. UX Mistakes to Avoid

❌ Too many animations
❌ Raw data dumps
❌ Inconsistent layouts
❌ Overcrowded screens

---

